   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The sixteenth year of Imperator Caesar Trajanus Hadrianus Augustus. Work done for five days on the dike works for the same 16th year at the desert canal, (2nd hand) Payni 21-25, on behalf of Tebtunis, (3rd hand) N.N. son of N.N. son of Tephersos, his mother being N.N. I, N.N., have signed.</ab>
         </div>
